cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Gemotion.jl: A Julia finite-element solver for steady two-dimensional Navier-Stokes-Fourier natural-convection problems with generalized material laws"
version: 0.1.2
license: "MIT"
type: software
abstract: "GeMotion.jl is a Julia finite-element solver for steady two-dimensional Navier-Stokes-Fourier natural-convection problems with generalized material laws. It is built on Gridap.jl and supports Cartesian Gridap models as well as named-boundary Gmsh meshes through GridapGmsh.jl."
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
authors:
